 eum-tickets-47225221910\n\nJoin Diaspora Dialogues and for a Literary Walk
 ing Tour through the Aga Khan Museum led by poet and authorSheniz Janmoham
 edand Aga Khan Museum Educator Laboni Islam.\nOn Sunday\, August 12\, 2018
 \, poet and author Sheniz Janmohamed and Aga Khan Museum Educator Laboni I
 slam will guide a Literary Walking Tour through the Aga Khan Museum. Take 
 inthe artistic\, intellectual\, and scientific heritage of Muslim civiliza
