UID:35784445239
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/dd-carousal-of-authors-publisher-s
 ponsorship-tickets-35784445239\n\nJoin the revelry as we fte DDs authors a
 nd playwrights\, both established and emerging\, and the new books and pla
 ys theyve produced through our mentoring and dramaturgy programs.\nLiterat
 ure as global as Toronto itself.\nThe evening will be a moveable feast of 
 sumptuous food\, the sultry sounds of live jazz\, and conversation so inte
 resting youll beg not to leave.\nDiaspora Dialogues Publisher Sponsorship:
  $5\,000\nEvery writer needs a publisher.\nThe dream of all writers is to 
 share their stories with the reading public. At this level\, you support t
 he critical workthat Diaspora Dialogues does through all our programming\,
  helping emerging writers develop craft throughintensive one-on-one mentor
 ship with some of Canadas best writers. Our public events provide unparall
 eled opportunity for writers to learn public performance skills\, and gain
  a professional writing credit\, while ourprofessional development program
 s helps them prepare for a successful careers in the arts.\nAs an Event Sp
 onsor at this level\, youll have premier acknowledgement on all of our med
 ia and marketing materials.Additionally\, youll receive 10 tickets to the 
 event\, which you can either use entirely for yourself and yourguests\, or
  donate back some (or all) to invite DD writers in your generous stead.\nR
 ecognition benefits include:\n Premier logo acknowledgement in materials f
 or the evening\, including eventsignage and program.\n Verbal recognition 
 from the podium.\n Recognition in press releases.\n Logo acknowledgement a
 s year-round supporter of Diaspora Dialogues\,including website\, posters\
 , postcards\, advertising and other print materialscreated\, and verbal re
 cognition from the podium in all events.\n 10 tickets to the event. If des
 ired\, DD will suggest writers to include in your ticketallocation.\n Tail
 ored broad-based social media campaign\nTax receipts for $4\,000 are avail
 able.\n**\nSponsorships at $2\,500 (wtih $2\,000 tax receipts) are availab
 le here:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/dd-carousal-of-authors-patron-spons
 orship-tickets-35784508428?aff=es2\nIndividual tickets at $400 (with a $30
 0 tax receipt) are available here:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/dd-carous
 al-of-authors-tickets-34559805308\n
LOCATION:Design Exchange\, 234 Bay Street\, Toronto\, ON M5K 1B2
URL:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/dd-carousal-of-authors-publisher-sponsorsh
 ip-tickets-35784445239
