 ting youll beg not to leave.\nDiaspora Dialogues Patron Sponsorship: $2\,5
 00\nEvery writer needs a patron.\nWriters have long needed patrons to sust
 ain them through the ups and downs of the creative process and life.\nSupp
 ort is both practical and symbolic\; with it\, you validate a writers life
