  special evening with up to three friends\, and well invite one or more Di
 aspora Dialogueswriters to attend as your guest.\nIf staying at home with 
 a good book is more your speed\, wed be delighted to direct your $2\,500 d
 onation to enablefive emerging writers from the DD mentoring programs to a
 ttend this special evening in your place. The menteeswould greatly appreci
 ate the chance to step away from the lonely computer\, and into the compan
 y of their peers andmentors.\nRecognition benefits include:\n Logo acknowl
 edgement in materials for the evening\, includingevent signage and program
 .\n Verbal recognition from the podium.\n Recognition in press releases.\n
